      "span_text": "For the detection of TBSA by GC/MS, we followed the procedure whereby a pentafluorobenzyl ester derivative of TBSA derived from sputum was made and analyzed by GC/MS using chemical ionization (CI) in negative mode detecting the characteristic mass fragment m/z 297.3 [CITATION_1] ."
